1 the church's official vision, mission, and slogan, reflecting his commitment to unity, purpose,
2 tradition, and progress; and
3 WHEREAS, 2025 marked the church's Centennial Celebration, a remarkable
4 milestone that honored the vision, perseverance, and faith of generations past while looking
5 forward with hope and purpose to the future; and
6 WHEREAS, Progressive Baptist Church commemorated this historic occasion with
7 a Centennial Anniversary Gala on November 15, 2025, and a Centennial Church
8 Anniversary Worship Service on November 16, 2025, both celebrating a century of spiritual
9 guidance and community impact.
10 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
11 does hereby commend and congratulate Progressive Baptist Church of Lafayette, Louisiana,
12 upon the celebration of its one hundredth anniversary and does hereby recognize the church's
13 century of faith, service, and spiritual leadership in the community.
14 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Dr.
15 Chad E. Nora, pastor of Progressive Baptist Church.
